# Vast Monitor Implementation Plan

> **For agentic workers:** REQUIRED SUB-SKILL: Use superpowers:subagent-driven-development (recommended) or superpowers:executing-plans to implement this plan task-by-task. Steps use checkbox (`- [ ]`) syntax for tracking.

**Goal**: Implement a full monitoring and recovery dashboard for Vast.ai servers within the Hermes HUDUI, including real-time GPU/System health, Token traffic analytics, and a deterministic 5-step recovery control panel.

**Architecture**: Hybrid Polling + SSE. A remote Python Agent on the server provides metrics and executes shell commands; HUDUI Backend proxies these requests with caching; React Frontend renders the dashboard and manages the recovery state machine.

**Tech Stack**: Python (FastAPI) for Remote Agent & Backend, React (Vite + Tailwind) for Frontend, SSH Multiplexing for Recovery.

